text: There are a bazillion things to do in my small town of Wadsworth. One thing you can do is ride horses on the moon and sing songs with Abe Lincoln in the bar. On top of that, I recommend eating a hundred gallons of ice cream at any local ice cream shop downtown. Some of the flavors that they have are out of this world! Additionally in the winter, I like to go over to a place called kill hill next to the main highway. The hill is up extremely high, you can see the whole world from there! It has to be at least a million feet tall!
translation: V mojem majhnem kraju Wadsworth je milijon stvari, ki jih lahko počneš. Ena od njih je jahanje konjev na luni in petje pesmi z Abrahamom Lincolnom v baru. Poleg tega priporočam, da pojeste sto litrov sladoleda v katerikoli lokalni slaščičarni v centru. Nekateri okusi so resnično neverjetni! Poleg tega pozimi rad grem na kraj, imenovan "hrib smrti," zraven glavne avtoceste. Hrib je izjemno visok, z njega lahko vidiš cel svet! Mora biti vsaj milijon čevljev visok!

text: There are so many different activities you can do in my small town of Wadsworth. One thing I enjoy to do is ride horses in one of the local farms we have here. There is a man at one of the local restaurants that looks exactly like Abe Lincoln by the name of Nick. At the local ice cream shop by the name of Dolce, they have at least 20 different flavors of ice cream and Italian ice. They are oh so delicious. In the wintertime, we love to go sled riding at one of the local hills. The hill we go to is right next to the highway and is at least 50 feet high. Its one of the best hills around to go sled riding at!
translation: Obstaja toliko različnih aktivnosti, ki jih lahko počnete v mojem majhnem mestu Wadsworth. Ena izmed stvari, ki jih rada počnem, je jahanje konj na eni izmed lokalnih kmetij, ki jih imamo tu. V eni od lokalnih restavracij je možakar po imenu Nick, ki izgleda natanko kot Abe Lincoln. V lokalni sladoledarni z imenom Dolce imajo vsaj 20 različnih okusov sladoleda in italijanskega ledu. So resnično zelo okusni. Pozimi radi gremo sankati na eno izmed lokalnih gričev. Grič, kamor gremo, je tik ob avtocesti in je visok vsaj 50 čevljev. To je ena najboljših hribov v okolici za sankanje!
